787
00:59:04,490 --> 00:59:05,950
Okay. That sounds good.

788
00:59:05,950 --> 00:59:07,750
Seong Wuk!

789
00:59:07,750 --> 00:59:09,140
- You can go home now.
- Okay.

790
00:59:09,140 --> 00:59:11,110
- Thank you.
- Good work.

791
00:59:11,890 --> 00:59:14,660
