01:00:17,170 --> 01:00:18,680
Huh?

803
01:00:25,020 --> 01:00:28,480
Mr. Jang, I think I found

804
01:00:28,480 --> 01:00:31,550
who Im Dong Hyeon was
with that day 15 years ago.

805
01:00:31,550 --> 01:00:33,540
<i>You found him?</i>

806
01:00:33,540 --> 01:00:34,920
Yes.

807
01:00:37,550 --> 01:00:40,020
I'm looking at them right now.

808
01:00:53,850 --> 01:00:55,700
Min Ho!

809
01:00:58,270 --> 01:01:00,250
Min Ho!

810
01:01:18,500 --> 01:01:20,230
Okay.

811
01:01:23,660 --> 01:01:25,850
When did you get here?

812
01:01:28,510 --> 01:01:30,250
Do you recognize me?

813
01:01:30,250 --> 01:01:32,160
Of course, I do.

814
01:01:32,160 --> 01:01:36,060
You're Sung Chul. The one I'm grateful for.

815
01:01:37,760 --> 01:01:39,260
Hyungnim.

816
01:01:41,760 --> 01:01:43,870
I found it.

817
01:01:43,870 --> 01:01:45,160
Pardon?

818
01:01:45,960 --> 01:01:47,400
But...

819
01:01:49,110 --> 01:01:51,210
I don't remember.

820
01:01:52,720 --> 01:01:55,550
I try to remember,

821
01:01:56,770 --> 01:01:58,290
but I can't.

822
01:02:04,190 --> 01:02:05,770
Hyungnim,

823
01:02:07,290 --> 01:02:10,300
I wasn't able to help you then.

824
01:02:11,340 --> 01:02:14,210
But I think I can now.

825
01:02:15,740 --> 01:02:17,990
Your son, Min Ho.

826
01:02:17,990 --> 01:02:20,080
This time...

827
01:02:20,080 --> 01:02:23,200
This time, I'll make
sure to find him for you.

828
01:02:25,300 --> 01:02:32,240
<i>♪ Before the darkness comes ♪</i>

829
01:02:33,410 --> 01:02:38,660
<i>♪ I would like to see you once more ♪</i>

830
01:02:38,660 --> 01:02:40,330
Thank you.

831
01:02:41,230 --> 01:02:43,170
I appreciate it.

832
01:02:43,170 --> 01:02:48,220
<i>♪ Even somewhere far away ♪</i>

833
01:02:49,750 --> 01:02:55,860
<i>♪ Even at this remote place ♪</i>

834
01:02:57,610 --> 01:03:02,680
<i>♪ You're nowhere ♪</i>

835
01:03:05,870 --> 01:03:10,680
<i>♪ Nowhere to be seen ♪</i>

836
01:03:13,810 --> 01:03:18,520
<i>♪ I should wait for you ♪</i>

837
01:03:21,810 --> 01:03:26,820
<i>♪ I should take you with me ♪</i>

838
01:03:26,820 --> 01:03:30,470
<i>♪ Until you and I
disappear into that sunset ♪</i>

839
01:03:30,470 --> 01:03:34,620
{\an8}<i>This is what Dong Su found out.</i>

840
01:03:34,620 --> 01:03:37,010
{\an8}<i>He's in danger.</i>

841
01:03:37,010 --> 01:03:39,410
{\an8}<i>Are you sure he's dead?</i>

842
01:03:39,410 --> 01:03:40,630
{\an8}<i>Can you live?</i>

843
01:03:40,630 --> 01:03:42,170
{\an8}<i>Hyungnim!</i>

844
01:03:42,170 --> 01:03:43,270
{\an8}<i>Over here!</i>

845
01:03:43,270 --> 01:03:45,650
{\an8}<i>Hyungnim, you went through a lot.</i>

846
01:03:45,650 --> 01:03:47,430
{\an8}<i>I'll take it from here.</i>

847
01:03:47,430 --> 01:03:50,020
{\an8}<i>Should we treat him first?</i>

848
01:03:50,020 --> 01:03:51,770
{\an8}<i>A financial treatment.</i>

849
01:03:52,730 --> 01:03:54,210
{\an8}<i>I guess you can't let anyone find out</i>

850
01:03:54,210 --> 01:03:57,540
{\an8}<i>about the thing that's more
